Rehearing Denied.

No. 359. No. 525. No. 543. No. 545. No. 351, Misc. Hiatt, Warden, v. Brown, ante, p. 103; Clement v. Woods, Housing Expediter, ante, p. 911; Jiffy Lubricator Co. v. Alemite Company, ante, p. 912; Carpenter v. Erie Railroad Co., ante, p. 912; and Ex parte Newstead, ante, p. 909.

The petitions for rehearing in these cases are severally denied.

Mr. Justice Douglas took no part in the consideration or decision of these applications.
